abstract: Burkina Faso cabinet disbands presidential guard that took hostage interim Pres Michel Kafando and prime minister, and discharges minister in charge of security; also forms commission to find those responsible for coup attempt.
lead_paragraph: The cabinet dissolved the elite presidential guard that took the president and prime minister hostage in a failed coup just weeks before elections.

headline.main: Burkina Faso: Coup Leaders to Be Tried
